Project test server
http://autoshop.heroku.com/

Clone project:
sudo apt-get install git curl
git clone git@github.com:hiddenfile/autoshop.git
cd autoshop //переход в каталог сайта

Create gem-set:
rvm --default use 1.9.2@autoshop --create

Install gems:
gem install bundler
bundle install

Install Passenger:
passenger-install-nginx-module
passenger start

Install PostgreSQL:
sudo apt-get install postgresql
sudo apt-get install pgadmin3
sudo -u postgres psql postgres
\password postgres
sudo -u postgres createdb mydb

Install Redis:
curl -O http://redis.googlecode.com/files/redis-2.2.2.tar.gz
tar xzf redis-2.2.2.tar.gz
cd redis-2.2.2
make
cp src/redis-server src/redis-cli /usr/bin
redis-server //Для локального использования
redis-server /path/to/redis.conf

Create db and test content:
rake db:create
rake db:migrate
rake data:reset_admin
rake data:add_content


